{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dc48671def","title":"在中共河南省委文教部座谈会上发言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"62418668b2","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":22,"articleId":"dc48671def"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"59a24082d1","name":"李索开"},{"id":"9ec5840208","name":"河南"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8c288062b7","type":"title","text":"在中共河南省委文教部座谈会上发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def"},{"id":"a35992dc17","type":"authors","text":"河南李索开","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def"},{"id":"37d519db9d","type":"subtitle","text":"(李索开：诗人，《奔流》编辑)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def"},{"id":"e2fb50db8a","type":"paragraph","text":"在政治上应对创作人员重视、关怀，过去是不够重视的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def"},{"id":"1fe8fe1c12","type":"paragraph","text":"文艺领导是行政式的，剧协成立，要添干部，听说条件有三：一、有一定业务水平；二、有一定服务能力；三、两个字——听话。庄义顺起草的剧协章程里有些规定（后说在记录中有此一说）。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def"},{"id":"60095480b5","type":"paragraph","text":"我们领导同志，对有些事不够虚心，明明处理错了不是党的事，非说是党的事不可，使人很不舒服，陈局长对别人提出的意见，就不虚心，将个人与党混为一谈，去年文联卫生工作曾受到郑州日报批评，局派任毅科长召集大家开会，嘉季同志叫局长看稿，先将本期内容打个草稿，说一说，就决定一个稿件的取舍，编辑部对这种审稿方式有意见。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def"},{"id":"ffbec6ca11","type":"paragraph","text":"我在开封宿舍里开收音机，程广说他爱人有病，竟叫小孩告诉我说：不叫我开收音机。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def"},{"id":"3fc295aa5b","type":"paragraph","text":" （根据记录整理）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def"},{"id":"32973f9081","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《苏金伞右派集团言论与作品》（河南省文学美术工作者联合会，1958年）。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def"}],"page":{"id":"778c33ee72","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dc48671def","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}